{"tid":1788657,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國眾議院通過《西藏政策與支持法案》","createTime":"2019-12-19T00:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T00:59:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3ffd38a8a494e2edb2e74659e5bb40b9b8e83d4c","tid":1788657,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:34:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498460-20191219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498460-20191219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6jRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=b3c728fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498460-20191219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7a61e00c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498460-20191219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1498460_1_L_20191219065554.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1498460_1_L_20191219065554.jpg&h=525563dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國會眾議院外交委員會，一致通過《西藏政策與支持法案》，要求加強美國現有法律對西藏人權的支持，捍衛藏人宗教自由。法案強調，達賴喇嘛轉世或繼任決定權，完全屬於藏人佛教界，若有中國官員干涉將面對美方經濟受簽證制裁措施。<br />\n<br />\n法案亦表示，在美國在西藏首府拉薩設立領事機構之前，中國不得在美國設立新的領事機構。<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院外交委員會主席恩格爾表示，北京已經表達計畫選出未來西藏宗教領袖，包括第15世達賴喇嘛。恩格爾批評中國政府要為藏人選出宗教領袖，而不是透過傳統方式決定，是違反基本宗教自由原則，令人難以置信。"},{"pid":"478f84f73eeed802585f2d2fb87601809d5d08db","tid":1788657,"uid":311583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenu